kenmore.description: Mostly clear. Winds northeasterly 20 to 25 km/h turning northerly 15 to 25 km/h in the evening.
Partly cloudy. Slight (30%) chance of a shower at night. The chance of a thunderstorm in the west during the evening. Winds northerly 15 to 25 km/h becoming light in the late evening.
Partly cloudy. Slight (30%) chance of a shower, most likely in the late morning and afternoon. Light winds.
Sunny. Winds west to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h becoming southwesterly 20 to 25 km/h during the afternoon then becoming light during the evening.
Sunny. Light winds becoming northerly 15 to 25 km/h during the day then increasing to 25 to 40 km/h during the afternoon.
Mostly sunny. Winds north to northwesterly 20 to 30 km/h turning west to southwesterly during the morning.
Sunny. Winds southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h shifting east to southeasterly during the day.
Partly cloudy. Light winds becoming southeasterly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning.

ipswich.description: Patchy fog early this morning. Mostly sunny afternoon. Light winds becoming northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h in the late afternoon then becoming light in the evening.

Partly cloudy. Medium (40%) chance of showers in the evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the late evening. Light winds becoming northwesterly 15 to 20 km/h in the morning then becoming light in the middle of the day.
Partly cloudy. Medium (40%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. Light winds becoming northwesterly 15 to 20 km/h during the afternoon then becoming light during the evening.
Sunny. Light winds becoming westerly 15 to 20 km/h during the day then becoming light during the afternoon.
Sunny. Light winds becoming northwest to northeasterly 20 to 25 km/h during the day.
Mostly sunny. Slight (20%) chance of a shower. Light winds becoming westerly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning.
Sunny. Light winds becoming easterly 15 to 20 km/h during the day.
